ps://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1635568%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-Kelly-Online-%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%259C%2592%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2588%25B0%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E7%258E%258B%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E5%259F%25BA%25E8%25BF%2594%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E6%25A0%25A1&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7dTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=6f57ec69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1635568%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-Kelly-Online-%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%259C%2592%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2588%25B0%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E7%258E%258B%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E5%259F%25BA%25E8%25BF%2594%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E6%25A0%25A1&h=daf2b2b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1635568/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-Kelly-Online-%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92%E8%AE%8A%E6%88%B0%E5%A0%B4-%E7%8E%8B%E7%B6%AD%E5%9F%BA%E8%BF%94%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E8%AD%B7%E6%A0%A1</a>"},{"pid":"d6a99009ee349ef91bb636d78205abf5fd1ad31b","tid":1712934,"uid":80972,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"d77443749a63f4b983f70df9002f406c1247c02c","tid":1712934,"uid":35031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa5dce238a391d76f1ae196fc1f924572ecd703f","tid":1712934,"uid":80972,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:55:52.000Z","msg":"HKTVMALL之前簽落，講左唔會續喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇話去到幾時"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:58:50.000Z","msg":"王維基facebook帖文全文：<br />\n傲慢的性格和離地的無知，令香港人經歷前所未有的痛苦、把香港由「購物天堂」打壓成「血浴戰場」，很多朋友三個月沒有一晚睡好。這段時間我也有一個困難的決定。<br />\n世界不可以因一人之錯而停頓。<br />\n<br />\n家人不可以因政見不同，而斷絕血緣關係。<br />\n公司不可以因政見不同，而解除雇員合約。<br />\n商業夥伴不可以因政見不同，而毀掉合約合同。<br />\n<br />\n香港電視從來都不是大財團。經過五年艱苦經營，累積虧損超過十億，舊年仍然虧損二億多元。我們沒有用不完的資源，但全力建立「真香港人」的大型網購平台。<br />\n<br />\n我們希望在未來兩年，做到收支平衡，才能在這裏抗衡其他香港以外的平台。去年底已落實在不同媒體渠道賣廣告，包括和TVB 簽訂2019年廣告合約，寫明全年最少支付的廣告費。今年上半年已經在TVB 有幾個廣告出街；下半年，按合約我們仍需面對剩下數百萬元的廣告費。<br />\n<br />\n我們不能毀約 ─ HKTVmall將在10月初開始，在TVB 播放新廣告。<span style=\"color: red;\">完成今年的廣告合約之後，我們會更小心決定明年的廣告策略。</span><br />\n我知道這個決定會令很多支持HKTVmall的朋友失望。但作為上市公司，我們對香港有社會責任，亦對所有信任我們的投資者、2800多個加盟商及1250名同事手足，有不可推卻的企業責任。別人的缺失，為什麼要一群為香港努力付出的「真香港人」承擔後果和懲罰？<br />\n我一直無忘初衷，無論承受多大的財政和政治壓力，仍堅持使命而拼盡全力。這次，我衷心希望會得到大家諒解。"},{"pid":"8be6be97504d4314677d23f54f68dda8889b222b","tid":1712934,"uid":142225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"99493fcaf3beae15f750794b1b203227394dc969","tid":1712934,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"59a2e8138459d6ca30210053bc8f49f2305af28d","tid":1712934,"uid":187363,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"王維基去左中大<br />\n仲有冇咩野要補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:56:31.000Z","msg":"炒撚左車啦 個位係副校長喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:59:26.000Z","msg":"不如試下睇真啲？"},{"pid":"0fd5dbdc1f5b424499733a46110809aa08e3d727","tid":1712934,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8be6be97504d4314677d23f54f68dda8889b222b","tid":1712934,"uid":142225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"99493fcaf3beae15f750794b1b203227394dc969","tid":1712934,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"59a2e8138459d6ca30210053bc8f49f2305af28d","tid":1712934,"uid":187363,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"王維基去左中大<br />\n仲有冇咩野要補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:56:31.000Z","msg":"炒撚左車啦 個位係副校長喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:59:26.000Z","msg":"不如試下睇真啲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:01:47.000Z","msg":